你說夠了嗎！
Would you stop saying that!

489
00:43:14,148 --> 00:43:16,187
-加里
-賴瑞
- Gary...
- Larry!

490
00:43:16,316 --> 00:43:18,985
看著不錯。有蘿勃塔的消息嗎？
That looks great.
Any word from Roberta yet?

491
00:43:19,110 --> 00:43:20,819
這麼快就搞上了，萊斯莉。
Fast work, Les.

492
00:43:20,946 --> 00:43:22,986
哦，這裡還有一些雞肉。
Oh, let's have some chicken.

493
00:43:23,115 --> 00:43:25,154
賴瑞，那是明天吃的。
The chicken is for tomorrow. Larry!

494
00:43:25,283 --> 00:43:27,193
員警怎麼說？
What did the police say?

495
00:43:27,327 --> 00:43:29,996
出了這麼大的事你們還吃東西！
I can't believe
you're eating during a crisis!

496
00:43:30,122 --> 00:43:31,532
我們夠緊張的了，你還要怎麼樣？
We're nervous!

497
00:43:31,665 --> 00:43:34,452
那你們應該像個正常人那樣去打鎮定劑！
Then take a Valium like a normal person!

498
00:43:39,672 --> 00:43:41,712
她有一口好牙。
She has great teeth.

499
00:43:42,592 --> 00:43:45,842
這就是我為什麼出現在炮台公園
(Dez)
That's why I showed up at Battery Park.

500
00:43:46,887 --> 00:43:51,182
吉姆說你的一個朋友摔死在
大西洋城的旅館外邊。
Jim said a friend of yours got killed
outside your hotel in Atlantic City.

501
00:43:51,308 --> 00:43:53,348
他擔心壞了。
He was pretty worried.

502
00:43:53,477 --> 00:43:55,517
摔了？
Killed?

503
00:43:55,646 --> 00:43:57,520
殺死了？
Dead?

504
00:43:57,648 --> 00:44:01,231
這也是你的興趣之一，是嗎，蘇珊？
Sort of goes with the territory,
doesn't it, Susan?

505
00:44:03,696 --> 00:44:05,736
也許我知道是誰幹的。
Maybe I know who did it.

506
00:44:07,407 --> 00:44:09,447
我希望我能想起來。
I wish I could remember.

507
00:44:11,662 --> 00:44:13,701
也許就是你殺的。
Maybe you were the killer.

508
00:44:14,540 --> 00:44:16,579
不可能。
No! (laughs)

509
00:44:21,922 --> 00:44:24,876
我想我要躺一會兒
I should probably lay low for while, huh?

510
00:44:25,467 --> 00:44:27,506
好主意。
It might be a wise idea.

511
00:44:29,304 --> 00:44:32,258
你不知道在碼頭的那個人是誰？
You don't know
who the guy at the quay was?

512
00:44:34,809 --> 00:44:36,848
也許是被你拋棄的情人
Maybe a jilted lover?

513
00:44:40,565 --> 00:44:42,605
肯定不是。
I don't think so.

514
00:44:45,445 --> 00:44:47,484
也有可能。
Maybe he was.

515
00:44:48,364 --> 00:44:50,487
你可知道
You know somethin'?

516
00:44:50,616 --> 00:44:53,237
你不完全是我所想的那樣。
You are not at all what I expected.

517
00:44:54,787 --> 00:44:57,325
你也不全是我想的那樣。
You're not quite what I expected either.

518
00:44:59,374 --> 00:45:01,414
薩克斯
(sax ophone)

519
00:45:18,768 --> 00:45:21,805
我怎麼認識的吉姆？我是說…
Just how did I meet Jim? I mean, how...

520
00:45:22,563 --> 00:45:24,603
我怎麼遇到他的？
How did I meet him?

521
00:45:24,733 --> 00:45:26,771
也許這個有幫助。
Maybe it would help.

522
00:45:26,901 --> 00:45:29,357
我想是在那個咖啡店裡。
I think it was at some coffee shop.

523
00:45:30,655 --> 00:45:32,694
那是你工作的第一天，
It was your first day at work.

524
00:45:32,823 --> 00:45:34,863
吉姆大搖大擺的進來。
Jim waltzed in.

525
00:45:34,992 --> 00:45:38,077
你給他帶來吃的，然後把帳單撕了。
You brought his food over
and you ripped up the check.

526
00:45:39,789 --> 00:45:43,074
他個高嗎？我說的是吉姆。
Is he tall? I mean Jim.

527
00:45:44,085 --> 00:45:46,326
中等個頭吧。
He's about medium.

528
00:45:47,838 --> 00:45:49,878
哪種身材？
Is he sort of thin?

529
00:45:51,300 --> 00:45:53,339
哪種，哪種，呃…
Sort of. Sort of, um...

530
00:45:54,261 --> 00:45:56,253
跟我差不多。
...my build.

531
00:45:59,933 --> 00:46:02,056
眼睛是什麼顏色的？
What colour eyes does he have?

532
00:46:06,273 --> 00:46:08,181
藍的。
Blue.

533
00:46:08,316 --> 00:46:10,356
跟你一樣？
Like yours?

534
00:46:17,241 --> 00:46:19,234
抱歉，抱歉。
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

535
00:46:19,369 --> 00:46:21,408
抱歉。
(Roberta whispers) Sorry.

536
00:46:22,788 --> 00:46:25,494
我不知道怎麼回事，只是…
I don't know what happened. I just...

537
00:46:26,292 --> 00:46:27,786
不好意思。
Sorry.

538
00:46:32,381 --> 00:46:34,420
雷聲
(thunder rumbles)

539
00:47:33,899 --> 00:47:35,939
哼哼
(groans)

540
00:47:43,867 --> 00:47:45,907
過來。
Come on.

541
00:48:08,141 --> 00:48:10,180
迪茲
(whispers) Dez!

542
00:48:11,019 --> 00:48:13,057
迪茲
Dez...

543
00:48:18,568 --> 00:48:20,607
和我一起吃早餐嗎？
Wanna go out to breakfast with me?

544
00:48:21,571 --> 00:48:23,610
早餐
Breakfast?

545
00:48:25,825 --> 00:48:28,742
你怎麼了？穿的有點噁心。
What have you got on?
Some sort of disguise?

546
00:48:28,869 --> 00:48:32,119
-你不喜歡？
-不，只是，呃…
- You don't like it?
- No, it's, uh...

547
00:48:32,247 --> 00:48:35,034
還是迷人的。
...sort of charming.

548
00:48:36,377 --> 00:48:38,119
我請客。
It's my treat.

549
00:48:39,296 --> 00:48:41,335
你要幹嘛？搶銀行？
What did you do? Rob a bank?

550
00:48:41,464 --> 00:48:44,382
我不知道，也許吧。
I don't know. Maybe.

551
00:48:46,136 --> 00:48:48,010
你要到哪裡去？
Where do you wanna go?

552
00:48:48,137 --> 00:48:50,379
看，我在手提箱找到這個。
See, I found this in the suitcase.

553
00:48:51,975 --> 00:48:54,015
Gunny的咖啡店？我知道這地方。
Gunny's Coffee Shop? I know the place.

554
00:48:54,143 --> 00:48:56,183
它在中央大街附近。
It's over on Center Street.

555
00:48:56,312 --> 00:48:59,099
也許我就是在那兒遇見吉姆的。
Maybe that's the place where I met Jim.

556
00:48:59,691 --> 00:49:01,019
-然後？
-然後…
- So?
- So...

557
00:49:01,151 --> 00:49:05,563
然後我們就去那裡
看看是否有人認識我。
So we go there
and see if anybody remembers me.

558
00:49:05,697 --> 00:49:08,946
看得怎麼樣，有熟悉的嗎？
So what do you think?
Anyone look familiar?

559
00:49:10,409 --> 00:49:12,651
還沒有。
No. Not yet.

560
00:49:21,420 --> 00:49:24,255
我在手提箱裡找到這個，你聽說過嗎？
I found this in the suitcase.
You ever hear of it?

561
00:49:24,381 --> 00:49:27,915
魔術俱樂部？是的，在百老匯附近。
The Magic Club? Yeah.
That's that place over on Broadway.

562
00:49:28,051 --> 00:49:29,379
怎麼了？
Why?

563
00:49:29,511 --> 00:49:32,216
我想我應該去那，看看有沒有熟人。
I thought I'd go there
and see if I remember anyone.

564
00:49:32,347 --> 00:49:35,052
-你知道你要點什麼嗎？
-當然。
- You know what you're having?
- Sure.

565
00:49:35,183 --> 00:49:37,223
你要點什麼？
What are you having?

566
00:49:37,352 --> 00:49:39,392
嗯，是你請客，對吧？
Well, it's your treat, right?

567
00:49:39,521 --> 00:49:41,513
是的，我付帳。
(giggles) Yeah, I got money.

568
00:49:41,648 --> 00:49:43,724
我要點…藍莓點心。
I'm gonna have... blueberry blintzes.

569
00:49:43,859 --> 00:49:45,897
很好，我也要那個。
I'll have that too. That sounds good.

570
00:49:46,027 --> 00:49:48,067
你要點什麼？
What can I get you?

571
00:49:48,196 --> 00:49:50,568
呃，一杯咖啡。
Yes, I would like a... coffee...

572
00:49:51,324 --> 00:49:53,696
還有…甜圈餅
...and a, uh... doughnut.

573
00:49:53,826 --> 00:49:58,073
小姐，如果你有空了，就給我們上吃的吧。
Miss! When you get a chance,
could you take our order?

574
00:49:58,206 --> 00:50:00,163
給你可以，她可不行。
You can stay. She's gotta go.

575
00:50:00,290 --> 00:50:02,829
Mick，那個穿夾克的瘋子女孩來了。
Mick, it's that crazy girl with the jacket.

576
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:04,999
-你，滾！
-你認識我？
- You, out!
- You know me?!

577
00:50:05,129 --> 00:50:07,252
對，別想在這兒吃霸王餐。
Yeah. You won't get a free meal here.

578
00:50:07,381 --> 00:50:10,750
-我有錢，我可以付款。
-我不要你的錢，滾出去。
- I got money, I can pay.
- I don't want your money. Get out.

579
00:50:10,884 --> 00:50:13,589
-我們有錢，怎麼了？
-想想你自己的事吧。
- We got money. What is it?
- Mind your own business.

580
00:50:13,720 --> 00:50:16,472
-這就是我的事，等一下。
-過來，出去。
- This is my business, wait a minute!
- Come on, out!

581
00:50:16,598 --> 00:50:19,302
-嘿，我和他一起的。
-出去，出去。
- Hey, I'm with her.
- Come on, come on.

582
00:50:20,810 --> 00:50:23,183
你幸運去吧，我沒向你逼帳！
You're lucky I don't press charges!

583
00:50:23,313 --> 00:50:24,938
迪茲。
Dez.

584
00:50:25,065 --> 00:50:27,638
你怎麼樣，還好吧？太對不起了。
Are you OK? Are you all right? I'm sorry!

585
00:50:27,776 --> 00:50:29,851
我說的第一條規則就是別給我找事。
Rule number one was no drama.

586
00:50:29,986 --> 00:50:33,153
-記得嗎？
-是的，我知道，抱歉。
- Remember?
- Yes. I know. I'm sorry.

587
00:50:34,657 --> 00:50:36,449
我們走吧。
Let's get out of here.

588
00:50:36,576 --> 00:50:38,154
不好意思。
I'm sorry.

589
00:50:52,341 --> 00:50:54,418
爭吵聲
(man and woman arguing)

590
00:50:54,551 --> 00:50:57,587
你從來不讓我戴眼鏡。
(woman)
You won't even let me wear my glasses!

591
00:50:57,721 --> 00:51:01,137
回去賣T?去吧，你被解雇了！
(man) Go back to selling T-shirts!
You're fired!

592
00:51:01,267 --> 00:51:04,433
不對，你錯了，藍，是我辭職不幹了。
(shouts) No, you don't, lan, because I quit!

593
00:51:06,563 --> 00:51:09,102
嘿，別在梯子下麵！
(Susan) Hey! Not under the ladder!

594
00:51:11,693 --> 00:51:15,821
我的命運絕不可能比這兒更糟糕的了。
敗類人渣！
My luck can't get much worse anyway.
Miserable scumbags!

595
00:51:16,573 --> 00:51:19,029
也許我應該在床上教訓他。
Maybe I should've slept with him.

596
00:51:19,159 --> 00:51:21,946
姐們，有個巫婆偷了我的衣服…
Man, some witch steals my clothes,...

597
00:51:22,079 --> 00:51:26,325
…米克爾被人從旅店窗戶扔了出去，
現在你又被炒了。
...Meeker gets pushed out a hotel window
and now you get fired.

598
00:51:26,458 --> 00:51:30,751
不太糟，但是壞運氣好像抓著你不放。
No offence, but bad luck really seems
to be following you around.

599
00:51:33,423 --> 00:51:36,756
我們現在都清閒了，一起去看個電影吧。
We're both free now.
Let's just go to the movies.

600
00:51:36,885 --> 00:51:38,923
兩場連映的？
A double feature?

601
00:51:39,053 --> 00:51:41,093
來吧。
Come on!

602
00:51:43,098 --> 00:51:45,851
如果你請我吃爆米花的話，電影票就我買了。
I'll pay for the movie
if you pay for the popcorn.

603
00:51:45,977 --> 00:51:47,554
可以，但是，爆米花多少錢？
OK, but listen. How much is popcorn?

604
00:51:47,686 --> 00:51:49,726
-2.50
-行。
- 2.50
- OK.

605
00:51:51,816 --> 00:51:53,855
笑
(giggling)

606
00:52:01,825 --> 00:52:03,864
就是這地方。
This must be the place.

607
00:52:03,994 --> 00:52:06,911
司機，靠邊停吧，就是這兒。
Sir, could you pull over, please?
This is it.

608
00:52:08,456 --> 00:52:10,496
真是不好意思。
I'm sorry about what happened.

609
00:52:11,292 --> 00:52:13,748
-你沒有生氣吧？
-沒。
- Are you sure you're not angry?
- Yeah.

610
00:52:14,587 --> 00:52:16,627
-真的。
-我沒生氣。
- Really?
- I'm not angry.

611
00:52:17,423 --> 00:52:19,463
你真夠哥們。
OK. You're a real pal.

612
00:52:20,885 --> 00:52:22,924
我會告訴吉姆的。
I'll tell Jim.

613
00:52:23,721 --> 00:52:25,631
-拜
-拜
- Bye!
- Bye.

614
00:52:32,856 --> 00:52:34,894
夠哥們，我會告訴吉姆…
A real pal. I'll tell Jim...

615
00:52:37,609 --> 00:52:39,768
布利克大街電影院
Bleecker Street Cinema.

616
00:52:49,913 --> 00:52:52,368
你只是別再這樣開除誰！
(man)
You just don't fire someone like that!

617
00:52:52,499 --> 00:52:54,575
我上哪裡去找這麼文靜的女孩去？
Who am I gonna find
at such short notice?

618
00:52:54,710 --> 00:52:56,749
拜託，你認識那麼多女孩。
Come on, Ray. You know lots of girls.

619
00:52:56,878 --> 00:53:00,793
-很多女人都在找工作。
-媽，別打擾我。
- (woman) Plenty of women need work.
- (Ray) Ma! Let me take care of this.

620
00:53:00,924 --> 00:53:02,003
你好。
Hello.

621
00:53:02,134 --> 00:53:04,007
你看見外邊的招工告示了？
You saw the sign outside?

622
00:53:04,135 --> 00:53:06,044
你是在找工作？
Are you looking for a job?

623
00:53:07,848 --> 00:53:09,923
是的，我想我是。
Yeah. Yeah, I think I am.

624
00:53:10,057 --> 00:53:12,216
-她還在想她在找工作。
-不。
- She thinks she's looking for a job.
- No!

625
00:53:12,352 --> 00:53:14,973
我是在找工作，是什麼工作？
I am, I am! What kind of job?

626
00:53:15,104 --> 00:53:17,227
進來吧。
Come on in.

627
00:53:17,356 --> 00:53:19,396
這位是雷。
This is Ray.

628
00:53:19,525 --> 00:53:21,564
-您好。
-這位是雷的媽媽，格蕾妲。
- Hello.
- This is Ray's mom, Gilda.

629
00:53:21,694 --> 00:53:22,809
嗨。
Hi.

630
00:53:22,946 --> 00:53:24,569
-這位是哈雷。
-嗨。
- This is Henry.
- Hi.

631
00:53:24,697 --> 00:53:26,072
您好，哈雷。
Hello, Henry.

632
00:53:26,198 --> 00:53:28,238
還有我，藍。
And I'm lan.

633
00:53:30,703 --> 00:53:32,660
收音機
(radio on)

634
00:53:43,299 --> 00:53:45,337
加里先生，你還好嗎？
Are you OK, Mr Glass?

635
00:53:45,467 --> 00:53:47,840
還行，謝謝你。晚安，Daisy。
Fine, thank you. Good night, Daisy.

636
00:53:47,970 --> 00:53:50,295
我希望加里夫人沒事。
I hope you get good news
about Mrs Glass.

637
00:53:50,430 --> 00:53:51,426
謝謝。
Thank you.

638
00:53:52,015 --> 00:53:54,007
你拿這個包去哪？
Where did you get this bag?

639
00:53:54,142 --> 00:53:56,182
它是我的，加里夫人把它給我了。
It's mine. Mrs Glass give it to me.

640
00:53:56,311 --> 00:53:58,350
把包給我，Daisy。
Give me the bag, Daisy.

641
00:53:59,147 --> 00:54:02,397
-Daisy，把包給我。
-對不起，這包是我的。
- Daisy, give me the bag!
- Sorry, you ain't getting this bag.

642
00:54:02,526 --> 00:54:05,691
-請你給我，我要好好的問問你。
-這包是我的。
- Please, I'm asking you nicely.
- You're not getting this.

643
00:54:05,820 --> 00:54:08,276
《笨蛋主持》
(# "Sucker MCs" by Run DMC
on ghetto blaster)

644
00:54:18,207 --> 00:54:22,454
嘿，我說，你們能挪個地方吃東西嗎？
Hey, guys. Could you, uh...
have your picnic somewhere else?

645
00:54:30,635 --> 00:54:32,675
嘿，你們這些人！
Hey, guys!

646
00:54:34,348 --> 00:54:35,723
好吧，
Right...

647
00:54:35,849 --> 00:54:38,304
小心輕放，行吧？
Just try to be careful, all right?

648
00:54:41,646 --> 00:54:44,897
聽著，我不想捲入家庭糾紛，好嗎。
Listen, I don't get involved
in domestic disputes, OK?

649
00:54:45,025 --> 00:54:46,851
不是糾紛。
There's no dispute.

650
00:54:46,985 --> 00:54:49,310
在她沒有失蹤前時，她穿著一件夾克。
She had the jacket on
when she disappeared.

651
00:54:49,446 --> 00:54:52,482
某種原因上講，這對她很不一樣。
It was very special to her
for some reason.

652
00:54:52,616 --> 00:54:54,691
你真的記不起來她了？
Don't you even remember her?

653
00:54:54,826 --> 00:54:56,866
你也記不起來夾克了？
Don't you remember the jacket?

654
00:54:56,995 --> 00:55:01,656
黑色的，上面還有一個金色的像金字塔的圖形
It was black and gold and it had
a sort of a pyramid thing on it...

655
00:55:01,791 --> 00:55:03,534
就像鈔票上的那樣。
...like on a dollar bill.

656
00:55:03,668 --> 00:55:05,708
記不清了。
Vaguely.

657
00:55:05,837 --> 00:55:09,003
