01:20:06,080 --> 01:20:09,414
他又開始找蘇珊了，她從墨西哥州回來晚了。
"He's looking for Susan again.
She's late returning from Mexico."

995
01:20:09,542 --> 01:20:11,499
這是他第五個啟事了。
"This is his fifth ad."

996
01:20:11,627 --> 01:20:14,961
為什麼他如此強烈的想要見她？
她是誰？
"Why does he want to see her so badly?
Who is she?"

997
01:20:15,089 --> 01:20:17,330
還有我的一張照片。
And there's my picture.

998
01:20:18,259 --> 01:20:21,425
加里，為什麼你不告訴我她讀了這些啟事呢？
Gary, why didn't you tell me
she read the personals?

999
01:20:21,553 --> 01:20:23,593
我們昨天就可以搞定了。
We could've settled this yesterday.

1000
01:20:23,722 --> 01:20:26,474
她一直都在看這些啟事。我不認為…
She read them all the time. I didn't think...

1001
01:20:26,600 --> 01:20:31,143
嗯，是。幸虧了每一個人，
我才能活下來想做點什麼。
Yeah, well, fortunately for everybody,
I'm here and I'm thinking.

1002
01:20:31,272 --> 01:20:33,310
把車鑰匙給我。
Give me the car keys.

1003
01:20:35,859 --> 01:20:37,982
我會把它完整帶回來的。
I'll bring it right back.

1004
01:20:38,111 --> 01:20:39,689
嘿咻。
Hiya.

1005
01:20:40,447 --> 01:20:43,401
加里。她拿的是你的汽車鑰匙。
Gary! She is taking the car keys!

1006
01:20:45,577 --> 01:20:48,364
別說了，萊斯莉，行嗎？
Shut up, Leslie. OK?

1007
01:20:49,497 --> 01:20:53,958
日記本。有點偷偷摸摸的感覺。
她是怎麼評論我的？
Diary. That little sneak,
what did she say about me?

1008
01:21:17,608 --> 01:21:20,893
瘋狂尋找
陌生人尋找蘇珊
"Desperately seeking
stranger seeking Susan."

1009
01:21:21,028 --> 01:21:25,275
敬啟者，在星期六晚9點半，百老匯魔術俱樂部見。
"Regarding key. Meet me Saturday night,
Magic Club, Broadway. 9.30pm. Be there."

1010
01:21:25,407 --> 01:21:27,613
-就這些了？
-她會喜歡的。
- Is that it?
- She'll love it.

1011
01:21:27,742 --> 01:21:29,782
去櫃檯付錢。
Pay at the cashier.

1012
01:21:33,832 --> 01:21:36,868
四十歲單身白人男性，
尋找下午的玩伴。
"Single white male, 40,
looking for afternoon playmates."

1013
01:21:37,002 --> 01:21:40,287
就這些了？去櫃檯付錢。
Is that it? Pay at the cashier.

1014
01:21:55,019 --> 01:21:56,846
迪茲…
Dez...

1015
01:21:58,814 --> 01:22:00,854
我不是蘇珊。
I'm not Susan.

1016
01:22:01,984 --> 01:22:05,068
我是家庭主婦，住在紐澤西李堡。
I'm a housewife
and I live in Fort Lee, New Jersey.

1017
01:22:05,946 --> 01:22:08,402
我已經結婚四年了。
I've been married for four years.

1018
01:22:08,533 --> 01:22:10,192
我丈夫加里…
My husband Gary...

1019
01:22:10,325 --> 01:22:14,489
他做浴盆和浴室的生意。
He sells bathroom spas and saunas.

1020
01:22:19,835 --> 01:22:21,875
你怎麼還是這樣？
You never stop, do you?

1021
01:22:22,003 --> 01:22:24,210
不，這是真的，真的。
No, really! Really!

1022
01:22:24,339 --> 01:22:28,966
這就是我喜歡你的原因，我從不知道你
下一句會說什麼，過來。
That's why I like you. I never know
what you'll say next. Come here.

1023
01:22:32,305 --> 01:22:35,259
-門鎖聲
-迪茲。
- (door lock rattles)
- Dez.

1024
01:22:37,978 --> 01:22:40,017
-那是什麼？
-不知道。
- What is that?
- I dunno.

1025
01:22:42,357 --> 01:22:44,396
有人想進來。
Someone's trying to get in.

1026
01:22:54,576 --> 01:22:56,569
哦，天啊。
Oh, my God.

1027
01:22:56,704 --> 01:22:58,697
哦，是吉姆。
Oh, my God, it's Jim.

1028
01:22:58,830 --> 01:23:00,870
天啊。
Oh, my God.

1029
01:23:03,836 --> 01:23:07,371
吉姆，吉姆。
Jim... Jim. Jim.

1030
01:23:07,839 --> 01:23:12,881
謝天謝地，你嚇壞我了。你覺得怎麼樣，啊？
Thank God. You had me worried.
How you doing, man? Huh? Huh?

1031
01:23:13,011 --> 01:23:15,882
有人打我了，一片黑。
Somebody jumped me. It was dark.

1032
01:23:16,598 --> 01:23:18,757
嗯，呃…
Yeah. uh...

1033
01:23:19,309 --> 01:23:21,348
是我幹的。
It was me.

1034
01:23:22,104 --> 01:23:24,641
我以為你是別人呢。
I thought you were somebody else.

1035
01:23:24,773 --> 01:23:26,812
你以為我是誰？
Who did you think I was?

1036
01:23:28,401 --> 01:23:31,984
有人跟蹤了蘇珊，我想你可能是他。
Somebody's been following Susan.
I thought maybe you were him.

1037
01:23:32,113 --> 01:23:34,070
誰跟蹤她？
Who's following her?

1038
01:23:34,198 --> 01:23:35,942
不知道。
I don't know.

1039
01:23:36,075 --> 01:23:37,867
你知道蘇珊。
You know Susan.

1040
01:23:37,994 --> 01:23:41,445
從她那裡得到一個清楚的答案真是困難。
It's really tough
to get a straight answer out of her.

1041
01:23:43,708 --> 01:23:45,701
她需要我，迪茲。
She needs me, Dez.

1042
01:23:45,834 --> 01:23:48,160
我想或許她準備安頓下來了。
I think maybe she's ready to settle down.

1043
01:23:48,296 --> 01:23:52,756
安頓下來？蘇珊？別扯了，吉姆。
Settle down? Susan? Come on, Jim!

1044
01:23:52,884 --> 01:23:55,968
她從沒有做過什麼安頓的事，
她不是那類人。
She'd never do that.
She's really not the type.

1045
01:23:56,094 --> 01:23:58,087
從什麼時候你這麼瞭解她？
Since when do you know her so well?

1046
01:23:58,222 --> 01:24:02,301
呃，我只是不能看見她安頓下來。
我是說，她太野性了。
Well, I just can't see her settling down.
I mean, she's too wild.

1047
01:24:02,434 --> 01:24:04,760
但是這也是她的魅力。
But that's what's so great about her.

1048
01:24:04,894 --> 01:24:06,472
是這樣嗎？
Is that so?

1049
01:24:06,604 --> 01:24:09,938
我是說，你真的好像對她做了一番檢查。
I mean, you really seem
to have examined this.

1050
01:24:10,651 --> 01:24:13,734
嗯，我們一起度過了一些時間。
Well, we've been spending
some time together.

1051
01:24:16,781 --> 01:24:19,533
可…你在說什麼呀，迪茲？
Just... what are you saying here, Dez?

1052
01:24:19,659 --> 01:24:21,069
啊？
Huh?

1053
01:24:23,538 --> 01:24:25,779
我不想對你胡說八道，吉姆。
I'm not gonna bullshit you, Jim.

1054
01:24:25,915 --> 01:24:28,999
是一件不好出口的事，
我沒說它沒有。
It was a shitty thing to do.
I'm not saying it wasn't.

1055
01:24:30,085 --> 01:24:32,872
但是你自己說她誘人的。
But you yourself said she was irresistible.

1056
01:24:35,216 --> 01:24:37,255
哦，不會吧。
Oh, man.

1057
01:24:37,384 --> 01:24:40,884
你，你為什麼不再打我一下，就像這樣的，
把我結果了？
W-why don't you just hit me again
and, like, finish me off?

1058
01:24:41,013 --> 01:24:43,053
-你看…
-啊？
- Look...
- Huh?!

1059
01:24:43,181 --> 01:24:45,720
別哭喊了。我真的為她而瘋狂…
Don't cry about it.
I'm really crazy about her...

1060
01:24:45,852 --> 01:24:47,843
…而且她也為我而瘋狂。
...and she's really crazy about me.

1061
01:24:47,978 --> 01:24:50,304
-我對不起，
-聽著，我瞭解蘇珊。
- I'm sorry.
- Listen. I know Susan.

1062
01:24:50,438 --> 01:24:52,645
無論她告訴什麼都是胡扯。
Whatever she told you doesn't mean shit.

1063
01:24:52,775 --> 01:24:56,938
她不是認真的，迪茲。我是知道的，
我追了她好幾年了。
She plays with people, Dez. I oughta
know, I've been chasing her for years.

1064
01:24:57,070 --> 01:24:59,442
我認為她跟我是認真的。
I don't think she's playing with me.

1065
01:24:59,572 --> 01:25:01,612
胡說。
Bullshit.

1066
01:25:02,367 --> 01:25:04,241
這樣吧，吉姆。
All right, Jim.

1067
01:25:04,369 --> 01:25:06,409
我們幹嘛不問問她呢？
Why don't we just ask her?

1068
01:25:08,957 --> 01:25:10,368
蘇珊。
Susan!

1069
01:25:10,500 --> 01:25:12,788
蘇…她在這兒？
Su...! You mean she's here?!

1070
01:25:14,170 --> 01:25:15,581
蘇珊。
Susan!

1071
01:25:15,713 --> 01:25:18,169
-到這兒來。
-蘇珊。
- Come on out here.
- Susan...!

1072
01:25:21,761 --> 01:25:23,801
蘇珊。
Susan!

1073
01:25:33,272 --> 01:25:35,312
她走了。
She's gone.

1074
01:25:37,235 --> 01:25:39,191
她就在這兒。
She was here.

1075
01:25:39,319 --> 01:25:41,359
我發誓。
I swear to God.

1076
01:25:41,489 --> 01:25:43,527
水壺鳴響
(kettle whistles)

1077
01:26:33,371 --> 01:26:35,411
迪茲，你在上面嗎？
(Jim) Dez, are you up there?

1078
01:26:36,833 --> 01:26:38,493
怎麼了？
Yeah?

1079
01:26:40,212 --> 01:26:43,296
猜猜怎麼了？
我想她把我倆都耍了。
Guess what, man?
I think she's jerking us both around.

1080
01:26:43,424 --> 01:26:45,048
你什麼意思？
What do you mean?

1081
01:26:45,174 --> 01:26:48,626
你看看吧，這個他媽的陌生人是誰？
Check this out.
I mean, who the hell is this stranger?

1082
01:26:48,762 --> 01:26:50,007
鼓
(drum roll)

1083
01:27:04,610 --> 01:27:07,279
蘇珊，我還是不明白我們來這兒幹什麼。
Susan, I still don't understand
why we're here.

1084
01:27:07,404 --> 01:27:09,694
信我吧，加里。你會驚喜萬分的。
Trust me, Gar.
You're in for a real surprise.

1085
01:27:09,824 --> 01:27:12,742
你的驚喜萬分已經讓我緊張了。
Your surprises are beginning
to make me nervous.

1086
01:27:12,869 --> 01:27:15,656
-她怎麼說？
-我們會驚喜萬分的。
- What'd she say?
- We're in for a real surprise.

1087
01:27:15,788 --> 01:27:18,243
我想我們在這兒看不到Tony Bennett。
I guess we're not gonna see
Tony Bennett here.

1088
01:27:18,374 --> 01:27:20,413
我應該叫員警跟著我們。
I'd settle for a police escort.

1089
01:27:20,542 --> 01:27:23,377
你怎麼能讓她穿上蘿勃塔的夾克？
How could you let her wear
Roberta's jacket?

1090
01:27:23,503 --> 01:27:27,632
嘿，她沒衣服了，總得穿點什麼吧。
Hey, she's cold.
She's gotta wear something.

1091
01:27:27,757 --> 01:27:30,130
為什麼你不把你的指甲剪了？
(dummy) Why don't you
cut your fingernails?

1092
01:27:30,260 --> 01:27:32,549
我聽不見你在說啥…
I can't hear what you're saying...

1093
01:27:32,679 --> 01:27:34,719
捂住叫喊
(muffled shouting)

1094
01:27:39,228 --> 01:27:43,177
迪茲，如果她看到我們倆都在這兒，
她很可能又一走了之。
Dez, if she sees us both here,
she'll probably just split again.

1095
01:27:43,315 --> 01:27:45,354
那你回去吧。
You could go home.

1096
01:27:45,483 --> 01:27:48,437
我要看看他媽的陌生人是誰。
I wanna see who this fuckin' stranger is.

1097
01:27:55,535 --> 01:27:59,615
讓我猜。三倍龍舌蘭到天亮。
Let me guess. Triple tequila sunrise.

1098
01:27:59,747 --> 01:28:01,823
薑味汽水。
Ginger ale.

1099
01:28:04,626 --> 01:28:06,536
你是威士卡。
And you're the Scotch.

1100
01:28:06,670 --> 01:28:08,580
這是你的。
This must be yours.

1101
01:28:08,715 --> 01:28:10,753
朗姆酒和Tab。
Rum and Tab.

1102
01:28:15,304 --> 01:28:18,174
坐著別動，我去找找陌生人。
Sit tight. I'm gonna
go look for the stranger.

1103
01:28:19,141 --> 01:28:21,180
什麼陌生人？
What stranger?

1104
01:28:21,310 --> 01:28:24,476
-天，她可真迷人。
-一坨漂亮的屎罷了。
- God, she's gorgeous.
- Beauty feces.

1105
01:28:37,575 --> 01:28:39,070
她在那。
There she is.

1106
01:28:39,202 --> 01:28:42,488
-哪？
-就在那兒，和買煙女說話的那個。
- Where?
- Right there. Talking to the cigarette girl.

1107
01:28:42,622 --> 01:28:45,409
那不是蘇珊。我之前從沒見過那個女孩。
That's not Susan.
I never even seen that girl before.

1108
01:28:45,542 --> 01:28:48,163
迪茲，那是蘇珊。你認為我能搞錯嗎？
Dez, that's Susan.
Don't you think I should know?

1109
01:28:49,086 --> 01:28:52,503
那可能是蘇珊，但不是我的蘇珊。
That might be a Susan
but that's not my Susan.

1110
01:28:52,632 --> 01:28:56,214
-那是我的蘇珊。
-那麼在巴特利公園的女孩是誰？
- That's my Susan.
- Then who was the girl at Battery Park?

1111
01:29:12,275 --> 01:29:14,268
誰是陌生人？
So who's the stranger?

1112
01:29:14,403 --> 01:29:16,478
吉米！
Jimmy!

1113
01:29:16,613 --> 01:29:18,653
誰是陌生人？
Who's the stranger?

1114
01:29:18,782 --> 01:29:21,273
-說來話長。
-嗯啊。
- It's a long story.
- uh-huh.

1115
01:29:21,409 --> 01:29:23,533
你怎麼也不會知道她的。
You wouldn't know her anyway.

1116
01:29:23,662 --> 01:29:25,701
-她？
-是，她。
- Her?
- Yeah. Her.

1117
01:29:28,458 --> 01:29:31,128
過來，找個私人空間去說話。
Come on. We'll talk about it in private.

1118
01:29:33,839 --> 01:29:35,877
敲門
(knocking)

1119
01:29:36,007 --> 01:29:38,628
我們還有三分鐘上場。
We've got three minutes before curtain!

1120
01:29:38,759 --> 01:29:40,799
戴上你的假髮馬上出發。
Get your wig on and get out there!

1121
01:29:49,144 --> 01:29:51,137
我在想蘇珊會不會出事。
I wonder what happened to Susan.

1122
01:29:51,272 --> 01:29:53,513
看起來像是你丟了女友。
Looks like you lost your girlfriend.

1123
01:29:53,649 --> 01:29:55,975
嘿，賴瑞，我結婚了，懂嗎？
Hey, Larry! I'm married, all right?

1124
01:29:56,110 --> 01:29:58,398
-哦，得了吧。
-怎麼？
- Oh, please!
- What?

1125
01:29:58,529 --> 01:30:00,569
樂隊聲
(band plays fanfare)

1126
01:30:05,327 --> 01:30:07,948
晚上好，女士們先生們。
Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

1127
01:30:08,079 --> 01:30:11,365
歡迎來到魔術俱樂部，我是主持人，雷。
Welcome to the Magic Club.
I'm your host, Ray...

1128
01:30:12,918 --> 01:30:15,788
酒吧生，給我結帳吧。
Bartender...
Can I have the check, please?

1129
01:30:17,422 --> 01:30:20,292
有誰從女皇區出來的嗎？
Hey, is there anyone out here
from, uh... Queens?

1130
01:30:20,425 --> 01:30:22,916
你。好的。我自己是從正常人家的肚子裡出來的。
You. Well, I'm from
normal parents myself.

1131
01:30:23,052 --> 01:30:24,250
零星笑聲
(scattered laughter)

1132
01:30:24,387 --> 01:30:28,799
是這樣的，今晚我們給大家一個特別的待遇。
Anyway, we got a special treat
for you people this evening.

1133
01:30:28,933 --> 01:30:31,389
讓我介紹一下獨一無二的，舉世無雙的…
Introducing the one, the only...

1134
01:30:31,852 --> 01:30:33,892
蘇珊，快上來。
Susan, get up here!

1135
01:30:34,022 --> 01:30:37,307
…還有他可愛的助手，Davina…
...and his very lovely assistant, Davina...

1136
01:30:37,441 --> 01:30:40,727
…今夜女王，鼓掌吧。
...Queen of the Night! So let's hear it!

1137
01:30:51,706 --> 01:30:54,909
加里，那是…
(Leslie) Gary... Is that...

1138
01:30:55,041 --> 01:30:57,533
不會吧。
It can't be.

1139
01:30:57,670 --> 01:31:00,505
我太喜歡了，真是好魔術啊。
I'm really enjoying this. It's a great trick.

1140
01:31:09,097 --> 01:31:10,889
蘇珊？
Susan?

1141
01:31:11,016 --> 01:31:13,970
-蘿勃塔？
-我不敢相信。
- Roberta?
- I don't believe it.

1142
01:31:14,727 --> 01:31:17,514
-蘿勃塔…
-加里，坐下。
- Roberta...
- Gary, sit down.

1143
01:31:25,196 --> 01:31:27,687
呃，我在這兒呆會兒，謝謝。
uh... I think I'll be staying, thank you.

1144
01:31:27,823 --> 01:31:29,401
鼓
(drum roll)

1145
01:31:51,263 --> 01:31:54,180
煙，要煙嗎？
Cigars? Cigarettes?

1146
01:31:56,393 --> 01:31:58,634
她還是很有型的啊。
She's really got style in a way.

1147
01:31:58,770 --> 01:32:00,810
她很不錯啊，加里。
She's good, Gary.

1148
01:32:02,441 --> 01:32:04,480
哦，對不起。
(Larry) Right. Sorry.

1149
01:32:27,215 --> 01:32:29,253
尖叫
(Roberta screams)

1150
01:32:42,562 --> 01:32:44,602
(screams)

1151
01:32:47,150 --> 01:32:48,977
哇哦！
Bravo!

1152
01:32:53,782 --> 01:32:56,451
是他，就是他。
